{"id":231285377,"title":"無痕生活之 #零碳時尚 #FashionRevolution","content":"#零碳時尚 #FashionRevolution\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/fNyL5Mk.jpg\n\n其實綠時尚、友善地球品牌在台灣也超級多啦！\n不要一直都說外國的時尚界才有環保意識了~~\n\n先來介紹一個超有權威的網站，\n教你很多資訊，\n例如：消費者可以怎麼做，才能改變時尚界的生態。\nhttps://www.instagram.com/fash_rev/\nhttp://i.imgur.com/FQiR638.jpg\n\n再來介紹台灣資源再利用的品牌：\nStory Wear - 從倫敦唸完碩士的創辦人，利用回收的牛仔布料，再次製造成新衣服！\n重點是不便宜，但超美！ \nhttps://www.ecochicmaker.com/pages/storywear\nhttp://i.imgur.com/JASh3Ex.png\nMijily - 主打「舊鞋回收換盆栽」的循環，讓物品再次找到價值~\nhttp://www.mijily.com.tw/Default.aspx\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/oiBaAKJ.jpg\n\n還有現在超紅的 Taptot App\n他們現在舉辦「零碳時尚穿搭選拔」，\n聽說有超多網紅響應，然後會往紅自己身上的衣服分享出來給投票者。\n也還蠻特別的~\nhttps://www.taptot.com/tw/zerocarbonfashioncontest/\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/QtRhJk8.jpg","excerpt":"#零碳時尚 #FashionRevolution，其實綠時尚、友善地球品牌在台灣也超級多啦！，不要一直都說外國的時尚界才有環保意識了~~，先來介紹一個超有權威的網站，教你很多資訊，例如：消費者可以怎麼做，才能改變時尚界的生態。","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"49eed176-a7ad-492c-b6cf-77733ab633ef","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-05-14T06:42:56.453Z","updatedAt":"2019-05-14T06:42:56.453Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":55,"tags":[],"topics":["愛地球","環保","網紅","免費","無痕生活"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{},"forumName":"無痕生活","forumAlias":"ecolife","school":"東海大學","department":"日文語言文化學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":55}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/fNyL5Mk.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/FQiR638.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/JASh3Ex.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/oiBaAKJ.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/QtRhJk8.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"79e29aff-9eca-44a2-ab02-53ea38c9c17b","url":"https://i.imgur.com/fNyL5Mk.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/fNyL5Mk.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/fNyL5